  "detailed_description": "In an attempt to create the perfect ping-pong.<br />\r\nAll movement in the game occurs in a circle. The goal is simple - do not skip the ball into your own goal and score the ball to the opponent.<br />\r\nA large number of settings and several game modes allow you to create that game - which you want and at the same time you can always find something new from other players.<br />\r\nAll action is accompanied by 8 bit music and few maps with different atmospheres.",
